{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Accessibility","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Glossary/Accessibility","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Web Accessibility (A11Y) odnosi się do najlepszych praktyk służących w celu utrzymywania strony internetowej przystępnej pomimo fizycznych i technologicznych ograniczeń. Web Accessibility jest formalnie określona i omawiana w <a href=\"/pl/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C</a> przez <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WAI\">Web Accessibility Initiative <small>(en-US)</small></a> (WAI).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"Learn more","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"General knowledge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility\">Accessibility resources at MDN</a></li>\n <li><a title=\"Web accessibility\" href=\"https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_accessibility\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web accessibility</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_web_accessibility","title":"Learn web accessibility","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Accessibility\">Learn accessibility on MDN</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://webaim.org/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">Web Accessibility In Mind</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_reference","title":"Technical reference","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">The ARIA documentation on MDN</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">The Web Accessibility Initiative homepage</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">The WAI-ARIA recommendation</a></li